{"tid":1186981,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日會怨恨自己以前鑑賞能力唔夠","createTime":"2019-06-05T10:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T10:43:37.000Z","uid":4618,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d158ec87a80a0ba04dd0f4599bd78e9e8114e989","tid":1186981,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"細個睇d經典作，淨係識得欣賞劇情張力，又或者唔知好睇在邊，入世未深理解唔到深刻主題，又或者會被時代價值左右，睇完冇乜反思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算大個睇返，都搵唔返第一次睇野種震撼，原來係致敬緊邊個前輩，原來係反映緊社會乜嘢狀況，原來係表達緊呢種感受，全部係眼界闊咗先明白到、體會到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愈大愈發覺無知係一種罪，可能未來嘅自己又會恨依家仲係睇緊面嗰浸，自己嘅膚淺係侮辱緊套作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fbeff703a1251d0a36c6746e02b1405d2870d6","tid":1186981,"uid":48579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"唔同階段睇嘅嘢緊係唔同<br />\n有乜好怨恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd23940dc660f73bd894bea00e61d37bb501109","tid":1186981,"uid":63311,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"係 中學拒絕好多普通女<br />\n但係中學後識執執就好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c2e72af21299a5afd4b1c4ca9da071e9cf262b","tid":1186981,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"43442164e3420fa35580071ed8e2f36944eebb85","tid":1186981,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54fbeff703a1251d0a36c6746e02b1405d287